<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Personal Webpage</title>
    <style>
        /* This is the CSS - It makes the page look pretty */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 4rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .content-section {
            padding: 2rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .content-section:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 2.5rem; }
        h2 { color: #2c3e50; border-left: 4px solid #3498db; padding-left: 10px; }

        .skills-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .skill-item {
            background: #e1ecf4;
            color: #39739d;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #777;
        }

        /* Simple button effect */
        .contact-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .contact-btn:hover {
            background: #2980b9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to My World</h1>
        <p>Innovator | Creator | Problem Solver</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>Hello! I'm [Your Name]. I'm passionate about building things that make a difference. This is my personal space on the web where I share my journey, projects, and thoughts.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>What I Do</h2>
            <ul class="skills-list">
                <li class="skill-item">Web Development</li>
                <li class="skill-item">Creative Design</li>
                <li class="skill-item">Data Analysis</li>
                <li class="skill-item">Strategy</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
            <p>Interested in collaborating or just want to say hi?</p>
            <a href="mailto:yourname@email.com" class="contact-btn">Send me an Email</a>
        </section>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 [Your Name]. Built with a touch of wit and Gemini.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
